* Persistence using sqlite
* Service termination when no clients or jobs running
* D-Bus interface needs some tweaks to allow IPP to run on top of it
  (e.g. handling option conflicts)
* Device scanning
* Prevent writes to read-only attributes
* Driver selection/assignment, e.g.
  http://cyberelk.net/tim/2010/10/26/choosing-the-best-printer-driver/
* Mapping PPD attributes (PageSize) to IPP attributes (media)
* Command line tools
* Filling in missing method implementations
* Limiting number of concurrent jobs
* Smart handling of job cancellation
